<view class="page notification-page"><view class="page-header"><text class="page-header__title">通知设置</text><text class="page-header__subtitle">仅展示当前真实可用的提醒设置</text></view><loading-skeleton wx:if="{{loading}}" rows="3"></loading-skeleton><empty-state wx:elif="{{error}}" type="error" title="通知设置加载失败" description="{{error}}" action-text="重新加载" bind:action="retry"></empty-state><empty-state wx:elif="{{!user}}" title="暂无通知设置" description="请完成用户初始化后重试"></empty-state><block wx:else><section-title title="默认提醒"></section-title><view class="settings-card"><settings-item title="默认提前时间" description="保存个人默认提醒偏好" value="{{reminderText}}" icon="notice" disabled="{{saving}}" bind:select="chooseReminder"></settings-item></view><section-title title="小程序内提醒"></section-title><view class="info-card"><view class="info-icon info-icon--active"><view class="info-mark"></view></view><view class="info-copy"><text class="info-title">动态页待处理</text><text class="info-description">有截止时间的任务会自动汇总到动态页，无需额外授权。</text></view><text class="available">可用</text></view><section-title title="微信订阅消息"></section-title><view class="info-card info-card--disabled"><view class="info-icon"><view class="info-mark"></view></view><view class="info-copy"><text class="info-title">微信消息提醒尚未开启</text><text class="info-description">完成订阅配置后，才可在微信服务通知中接收重要提醒。</text></view><text class="unavailable">暂不可用</text></view><view class="notice"><text>提醒能否送达会受到微信订阅授权、网络状态和系统设置影响。</text></view></block></view>
